elements state state Element
state &state.purpose;
&state.synopsis.gen; Description
A State is the name or postal abbreviation for a state (or province) in an Address.
Processing expectations
&format.inline; In an Address, this element may inherit the verbatim qualities of an address.
&state.parents.gen; &state.children.gen;
See Also &state.seealso.gen;
Examples
For examples, see &state.example.seealso.gen;.
